  "body": "We need to remove the last few references to `gopkg.in/yaml.v2`:\n\n```\ncmd/helm/repo.go\n28:     \"gopkg.in/yaml.v2\"\n\nglide.yaml\n12:- package: gopkg.in/yaml.v2\n\nglide.lock\n310:- name: gopkg.in/yaml.v2\n\npkg/lint/rules/template.go\n30:     \"gopkg.in/yaml.v2\"\n\npkg/repo/index.go\n24:     \"gopkg.in/yaml.v2\"\n\npkg/repo/index_test.go\n28:     \"gopkg.in/yaml.v2\"\n\npkg/repo/repo.go\n30:     \"gopkg.in/yaml.v2\"\n```\n\nThese should be replaced with `github.com/ghodss/yaml`, which exposes mostly the same API.\n",
